# Game Logos

Place your game logo images here with the following naming convention:
- game-slug.png (e.g., roblox.png, fortnite.png, valorant.png)

Recommended specifications:
- Format: PNG with transparency
- Size: 256x256px or 512x512px
- Aspect ratio: 1:1 (square)

Example structure:
/public/games/
  ├── roblox.png
  ├── fortnite.png
  ├── valorant.png
  ├── gta-v.png
  ├── minecraft.png
  └── lol.png
